{"lastModified":1761558772028,"uri":"c::10923570597::vessel::6b3dcd70-df43-11ef-aca5-71e1b7961b18","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area:\nKomodo National Park, Flores Island, and East Nusa Tenggara\n\nLamain Voyages II, a stunning Phinisi built in 2022, the epitome of Indonesian luxury. This floating haven welcomes 16 guests in 8 elegant cabins, each with an en-suite bathroom for ultimate comfort.\n\nYour adventure unfolds across diverse landscapes, from volcanic islands fringed by pristine beaches to vibrant coral reefs teeming with life. Witness the iconic Komodo dragons, graceful manta rays soaring through crystal-clear waters, and the mesmerizing sunset flight of thousands of bats.\n\nDive deep into the underwater world from the convenient and secure dive platform, tailored for both experienced divers and curious beginners. Explore hidden reefs, encounter a kaleidoscope of marine life, and create memories that will last a lifetime.\n\nBeyond the dive platform, adventures abound. Hike through lush landscapes, snorkel alongside colorful fish, or simply relax on the spacious top deck, soaking up panoramic views and refreshing breezes. Enjoy complimentary non-alcoholic drinks and snacks as you lose yourself in the beauty of the surroundings.\n\nThe spacious dining room and bar area become your haven for enjoying delicious meals and memorable moments with fellow travelers. Lamain Voyages II caters to your desires, offering flexibility to adjust the itinerary and ensure your dream vacation becomes reality.\n\nThis intimate experience, limited to maximum 16 guests, allows for personalized attention and deeper connections with the wonders of Komodo. Lamain Voyages II isn’t just a trip; it’s your gateway to paradise. Contact us today and start planning your unforgettable Indonesian escape!","blueprint":{"name":"LAMAIN II","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::6b3dcd70-df43-11ef-aca5-71e1b7961b18::assets::0aae0950-df45-11ef-9909-af7f5c675be6/{imageVa